01:56:58.743 --> 01:56:58.960
The Bible.

01:56:58.960 --> 01:57:00.983
This one's waterproof; Diana got this for me.

01:57:17.359 --> 01:57:18.159
You can take this outside and read it in the rain and it won't mess up.

01:57:18.159 --> 01:57:26.892
I think it's neat.

01:57:26.892 --> 01:57:33.419
