01:57:33.419 --> 01:57:38.519
' You can actually submerge this in water and it won't mess up.

01:57:38.519 --> 01:57:45.679
I got it for one of my family members in case they get left in the end times.

01:57:45.679 --> 01:59:04.480
I got this so they could have it for their cave because they're going to burn the Bibles really fast.

01:59:04.480 --> 02:00:01.440
