02:00:56.500 --> 02:01:00.879
You can't even tear the pages or wrinkle it.

02:01:10.183 --> 02:01:10.617
It's very hard to tear it up.

02:01:19.599 --> 02:01:29.554
I bet it would be hard for them to burn, too.

02:01:29.554 --> 02:02:13.598
Well, it probably could burn easily, but it's waterproof.

02:02:13.598 --> 02:02:25.563
She got it on Amazon, so I thought, 'Hey, why not?

02:02:25.563 --> 02:02:56.274
' You can dump water on it.

02:02:56.274 --> 02:02:58.103
I'll show you.

02:04:04.595 --> 02:04:05.433
See?

02:04:12.180 --> 02:04:13.040
It wipes right off and it's still dry.

02:04:13.040 --> 02:04:14.907
Pretty neat, huh?

02:04:14.907 --> 02:04:48.888
I thought I got it on my carpet.

02:05:39.199 --> 02:05:39.462
I try to think outside the box because I've seen so much, and I always try to think about people that get left.

02:05:42.960 --> 02:05:46.543
I go, 'Oh, man, they're going to have a hard time.

02:05:46.543 --> 02:05:50.300
We have to make it easier for them.

02:05:50.300 --> 02:05:53.698
Let's get them a waterproof Bible.

02:05:53.698 --> 02:05:57.636
' Maybe have some yeast for the bread and the tower gardens.

02:06:19.599 --> 02:06:19.999
But I feel the anointing of the Holy Spirit right now.

02:06:19.999 --> 02:06:21.599
Isn't that interesting?

02:06:21.599 --> 02:06:24.186
Father, we just thank You.

02:06:24.186 --> 02:06:38.388
Father, I thank You, Lord, for Your body that was broken for us.

02:06:38.388 --> 02:06:43.726
