02:06:44.891 --> 02:06:45.280
It's getting late.

02:06:45.280 --> 02:06:48.720
Father, I thank You for the body.

02:07:00.400 --> 02:07:00.640
I thank You, Father, that You've healed me and made me whole.

02:07:01.120 --> 02:07:04.100
I thank You for my family and for protection.

02:07:04.100 --> 02:07:07.946
I thank You, Father, that You watch over us.

02:07:07.946 --> 02:07:20.456
I thank You, Lord, that no matter how much persecution—You said we would be persecuted for the Word's sake—nobody has all the answers.

02:07:20.456 --> 02:07:44.960
Nobody knows everything, but Father, the parts that we do know, we do our best at sharing.

02:07:44.960 --> 02:08:12.877
Even that could be off, but at least we're trying.

02:09:23.872 --> 02:09:24.216
As long as we're seeking You, Father, I've learned to maintain humility.

02:09:24.216 --> 02:09:27.944
Do not get off in left field.

02:09:27.944 --> 02:09:42.284
Father, we thank You, Lord, for true humility, not for false humility trying to convince people that you're humble.

02:09:42.284 --> 02:09:45.017
True humility is displayed by the Holy Ghost.

02:09:50.420 --> 02:09:50.690
You know it versus ones that don't.

02:10:07.920 --> 02:10:11.383
I thank You, Father, for everybody represented here tonight.

02:10:55.120 --> 02:11:02.079
I thank You that You took care of all of us on that cross, and what You did was beautiful.

02:11:02.079 --> 02:11:14.400
We give You all the glory, honor, and praise, Father, for healing our bodies tonight in Jesus' name.

02:11:14.400 --> 02:11:15.040
Amen.

02:11:15.040 --> 02:11:21.199
Lord, we thank You for the blood.

02:11:21.199 --> 02:11:30.560
We make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

02:11:30.560 --> 02:11:32.834
I apply the blood over us.

02:11:32.834 --> 02:11:39.119
We thank You, Father, for the blood, for Your goodness, and for Your mercy.

02:11:39.119 --> 02:11:44.502
We plead the blood over us and cover ourselves in the blood.

02:11:44.502 --> 02:11:48.850
When you make much of the blood, the blood makes much of you.

02:11:48.850 --> 02:11:56.586
We thank You, Lord—uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

02:11:56.586 --> 02:12:04.377
Father, I ask You to speak through my vocal cords and think through my mind.

02:12:04.377 --> 02:12:09.291
None of me and all of You.

02:12:09.291 --> 02:12:55.790
I plead the blood over my eyes that if there's anything You want to show us tonight to warn us of that which is to come, Father, I'm here for You.

02:12:55.790 --> 02:12:57.409
If not, it's okay.

02:12:57.409 --> 02:13:00.525
Either way, Lord, we put ourselves in Your hand.

02:13:00.525 --> 02:13:36.000
We thank You, Lord, that You've called us and chosen to use us for such a time as this.

02:13:36.000 --> 02:13:40.400
We bless everybody that's here tonight in the mighty name of Jesus.

02:13:40.400 --> 02:13:51.091
Amen and amen.

02:13:51.091 --> 02:13:59.626
Take the blood.

02:14:18.739 --> 02:14:19.119
You know, it's my favorite topic.

02:14:19.119 --> 02:15:15.589
Braden and I talk a lot about this and the things the Lord shows me about the Nephilim and the thousand-year reign.

02:15:15.599 --> 02:15:29.280
He shows me a lot, and that's Braden's favorite topic.

02:15:29.280 --> 02:15:46.433
He loves to go over the sci-fi things, the way-out-there stuff, because it's stuff I can't explain.

02:15:54.906 --> 02:16:05.040
The things I see about what happens after the thousand years is over, the Lord will allow me to see.

02:16:05.040 --> 02:16:33.040
I've only had one really cool experience of that, but I know when the thousand years is over, He has so much for us to do.

02:16:33.040 --> 02:16:42.868
We're just barely getting started at a thousand years, and most people think it's all over.

02:16:42.868 --> 02:16:45.119
