02:16:52.019 --> 02:16:52.269
The Bible doesn't say.

02:16:52.269 --> 02:17:14.851
That's why Brandon doesn't talk about it, because I can't back it with scripture, and people will throw you under a bus.

02:17:14.851 --> 02:18:04.319
