02:20:39.760 --> 02:20:42.411
It's our turn to go tubing.

02:20:42.411 --> 02:20:43.096
Yes.

02:20:43.096 --> 02:20:45.543
Okay, well, that's fine.

02:20:45.543 --> 02:20:49.509
At least they like to pray.

02:20:55.520 --> 02:20:57.374
I have slow mode on too.

02:20:57.374 --> 02:22:44.560
Nowhere in the Bible does it say that your partner will automatically be saved.

02:22:44.560 --> 02:23:13.440
All must profess.

02:23:13.440 --> 02:23:24.320
If your unsaved loved one does not confess Jesus Christ as their Lord and personal Savior, they're in trouble.

02:23:24.320 --> 02:23:34.640
They can't go by your revelation in your relationship.

02:23:34.640 --> 02:23:40.400
You must know Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior by yourself.

02:23:40.400 --> 02:23:47.480
You will stand before the Father; no one else will stand for you.

02:23:47.480 --> 02:23:50.500
You must know Jesus Christ personally.

02:23:50.500 --> 02:24:03.133
Every single person, even my son, even my daughter, you must know Jesus for yourself.

02:24:03.133 --> 02:24:26.183
It's appointed unto man once to die and after that the judgment.

02:24:26.183 --> 02:24:31.148
No man without Jesus Christ will go before the Father.

02:24:31.148 --> 02:24:37.698
Unless a man is born again, he cannot enter the kingdom of God.

02:24:37.698 --> 02:24:43.915
He is the only way to the Father.

02:24:43.915 --> 02:25:14.790
Not Buddha, not Muhammad, not any other thing.

02:25:14.800 --> 02:25:45.280
Jesus is the only way.

02:25:45.280 --> 02:25:50.114
No false god in India—only Jesus.

02:25:51.669 --> 02:25:54.650
The Bible does not say we are learning.

02:26:07.010 --> 02:26:07.260
It's funny because I don't realize how many people have so many different theologies and beliefs until I start looking at things.

02:26:23.280 --> 02:26:23.669
What is your question with fireworks?

02:26:23.669 --> 02:26:26.297
She didn't ask a question.

02:26:26.297 --> 02:26:26.891
Fireworks.

02:26:26.891 --> 02:26:28.800
I don't see a question.

02:26:28.800 --> 02:26:35.182
Answer: What is tubing?

02:26:35.182 --> 02:26:48.062
