02:26:48.062 --> 02:26:58.320
Tubing is—I always call it like going down the river with Jesus.

02:26:58.320 --> 02:27:01.439
It's like a lazy river.

02:27:01.439 --> 02:27:09.915
Going tubing is like when you get in the river of life and you're praying.

02:27:09.915 --> 02:27:43.822
It's my way of having fun; I always call it "tubing" in my house.

02:27:43.822 --> 02:28:11.271
"We're going to go tubing; let's go pray.

02:28:11.271 --> 02:28:20.171
" When you go in the lazy river in Oklahoma—we have rivers, so people go tubing—they get their inner tube and a soda.

02:28:20.171 --> 02:28:31.280
Usually, rednecks get beers and listen to their waterproof radio.

02:28:31.280 --> 02:28:57.984
They go out there with their waders on, hanging out, fishing, and going noodling to catch catfish.

02:28:57.984 --> 02:30:00.460
So it's just a way of saying we're going to go tubing; it's fun.

02:30:07.879 --> 02:30:08.139
We're going to go hang out with Jesus.

02:30:08.139 --> 02:30:18.320
Yes, all the children under 20, until the age of accountability, which is 15—I saw all of them were taken in the Rapture.

02:30:19.560 --> 02:30:28.080
The parents were hysterical, trying to find their kids, but anybody above the age of 15 who didn't accept Jesus Christ was left.

02:30:32.263 --> 02:31:01.108
The kids were all taken—children who were not yet at the age of accountability.

02:31:01.108 --> 02:31:05.314
There are a lot of questions.

02:31:05.314 --> 02:31:26.777
I try to catch some every once in a while; I like some of them, and some I just ignore.

02:31:26.777 --> 02:31:27.920
It goes fast.

02:31:27.920 --> 02:31:30.045
Please like and subscribe.

02:31:30.045 --> 02:32:00.160
A lot of people thought it was 3i, and that's when I saw into it and kept seeing that thing come, but the Lord said it's not 3i.

02:32:00.160 --> 02:32:01.120
It's what's coming.

02:32:01.120 --> 02:32:04.898
This is like birthing pains, like an appetizer.

02:32:04.898 --> 02:32:09.051
Everybody's focused on it, but it's a distraction.

02:32:11.005 --> 02:32:23.371
The Lord said this will end up turning into nothing, but it's what's coming that they're not paying attention to.

02:32:23.371 --> 02:32:36.920
They're not talking about the major event that's about to take place.

02:32:36.920 --> 02:32:43.390
That's why he said to go back to the Oral Roberts video, "The Last Call.

02:32:43.390 --> 02:33:18.340
" Brazil was on the water, and I saw a major revival coming to Brazil—that's on the lower side.

02:33:24.206 --> 02:33:24.594
And then, what was the other one?

02:33:24.594 --> 02:33:25.760
Oh, Chile.

02:33:25.760 --> 02:34:11.316
How do you sow to the thousand-year reign?

02:34:11.326 --> 02:34:19.500
How do you sow to the thousand-year reign?

02:34:19.500 --> 02:34:34.048
What do you mean, financially, to get a better position in the thousand-year reign?

02:34:34.048 --> 02:34:57.115
Do everything you do in word and in deed to the glory of God.

02:34:57.115 --> 02:35:22.423
If you are doing it for show—well, those who sow in private will reap openly.

02:35:22.423 --> 02:35:35.747
Everything you do, do unto God, but don't do it for man's praise.

02:35:35.747 --> 02:36:17.179
If you get praise here, you won't get praise there.

02:36:17.179 --> 02:36:25.720
You must do it when nobody is watching you and without wanting them to give you applause.

02:36:25.720 --> 02:36:56.266
If I got applause here, you aren't getting applause there; it's for the thousand years.

02:36:57.772 --> 02:37:09.675
I try to do everything—even the bathrooms.

02:37:09.675 --> 02:37:26.230
Do something that is really detested by your flesh.

02:37:26.240 --> 02:38:20.907
Maybe you don't like mowing the grass or pulling weeds; go do it for the church and don't ask for any kind of reward or tell anybody about it.

02:38:20.907 --> 02:38:22.613
"Look at me!

02:38:22.613 --> 02:38:33.760
I just want to let you all know I volunteered at the church and gave my time to the nursery.

02:38:33.760 --> 02:38:51.760
" I want everybody to know I was special at the nursery and did all this for free for the last 10 years.

02:38:51.760 --> 02:38:54.630
Don't tell anybody; I did it for Jesus.

02:39:05.120 --> 02:39:05.460
I picked up the trash in the parking lot and did it for Him.

02:39:21.200 --> 02:39:21.520
I was the golf cart guy that brought people up from the front when it was cold.

02:39:22.160 --> 02:39:30.044
I was out there waving my stick, parking cars when it was freezing, but I didn't ask for praise from anybody.

02:39:30.044 --> 02:39:53.626
Or I gave this to the homeless guy on the side of the road and didn't have my camera out so I could put it on social media how great I was: "Look at this guy, he's really hurting.

02:39:53.626 --> 02:39:55.760
Let me get him some McDonald's.

02:39:55.760 --> 02:39:58.411
Oh, brother, aren't you having a hard time?

02:40:03.200 --> 02:40:04.560
" And they're filming it and putting it on YouTube to get likes, subscribers, and comments.

02:40:04.560 --> 02:40:05.700
It's baloney.

02:40:05.700 --> 02:40:15.359
Do it without having people tell you how great you are.

02:40:15.359 --> 02:40:16.399
Who cares?

02:40:16.399 --> 02:40:17.092
Deflect.

02:40:17.092 --> 02:40:38.661
The more you deflect and bring the glory to Him, doing it out of humility rather than pride, the more you'll get rewarded in the thousand-year reign.

02:40:38.661 --> 02:40:49.829
It's sad; they don't teach that at church because people don't know what the thousand years is.

02:40:49.829 --> 02:40:53.189
So yes, still the weird twilight and the birds.

02:40:53.189 --> 02:41:01.200
Brandon, do you remember the weird twilight, the birds, and the deer acting different?

02:41:01.920 --> 02:41:02.640
The breeding patterns?

02:41:02.640 --> 02:41:05.070
I still think about that.

02:41:05.070 --> 02:41:08.320
Something is going to happen with the sun.

02:41:08.320 --> 02:41:12.000
There's going to be some kind of haze over the Earth's atmosphere.

02:41:25.973 --> 02:41:26.222
I saw that the animals and the migrations in the days ahead will be altered.

02:41:26.222 --> 02:41:35.354
They'll start breeding when they're not supposed to.

02:41:35.354 --> 02:41:56.377
For example, the rut for deer in Oklahoma is usually in November, but I saw them starting to breed and having the rut in September.

02:41:59.000 --> 02:42:04.260
That throws off the babies when they're born; you want spring babies, not winter babies.

02:42:04.260 --> 02:42:06.373
It's dangerous for the mama deer.

02:42:06.373 --> 02:42:09.451
I saw the birds migrating too early.

02:42:09.451 --> 02:42:30.115
I saw a haze and it messed with people's minds—you know how people overcome sadness?

02:42:30.115 --> 02:42:46.309
I saw the fog; it made the plants stop growing right and threw the cycle of life off.

02:42:46.309 --> 02:42:46.994
No boasting.

02:42:46.994 --> 02:42:48.914
Keep your boasting to none.

02:42:48.914 --> 02:42:55.271
You have to seek Jesus without having people tell you how great you are.

02:42:55.271 --> 02:42:56.302
Jesus is great.

02:42:56.302 --> 02:43:04.960
Do I think college is worth it?

02:43:18.080 --> 02:43:20.105
It depends.

02:43:20.105 --> 02:43:31.227
Diana has a Master's degree.

02:43:31.227 --> 02:43:38.395
She graduated Summa Cum Laude.

02:43:38.395 --> 02:44:09.496
She graduated top of her class for both her Bachelor's and her Master's and is still the smartest person I've ever met.

02:44:09.908 --> 02:44:15.520
But she only uses it every once in a while.

02:44:15.520 --> 02:44:19.240
What is God telling you to do?

02:44:19.240 --> 02:44:24.319
Do you feel God has told you to go to college?

02:44:24.319 --> 02:44:33.085
If you're doing it to make money, I would not do that.

02:44:46.740 --> 02:44:48.590
I would pursue God and ask Him what He wants to do with my life before I have some harebrained idea like, "I think I'm going to be an architect.

02:44:48.590 --> 02:44:54.630
" Was that God?

02:45:25.760 --> 02:45:25.920
No, that's flesh.

02:45:25.920 --> 02:45:45.717
Everything you do, pray and fast and ask God what you're supposed to do.

02:45:55.187 --> 02:45:55.653
Now, will she use her degree in the future for our ministry?

02:45:55.653 --> 02:45:56.587
Yes.

02:46:09.920 --> 02:46:10.140
I know why God told her to do that now.

02:46:10.140 --> 02:46:15.451
Back then, I thought, "What in the world are we doing this for?

02:46:15.451 --> 02:46:26.522
" At the time, I thought we were doing church finances, but now our church is online.

02:46:26.522 --> 02:46:59.851
This is our church, and we're believing God for partners, but I've never asked for a dime.

02:46:59.851 --> 02:47:08.059
I know that eventually we'll have a congregation or a big ministry and she'll use it.

02:47:13.520 --> 02:47:17.880
We see what God is doing, and this has really taken off now.

02:47:17.880 --> 02:47:21.160
